{"tid":1128760,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱屌到我個00後籃波撚朋友跪低","createTime":"2019-04-28T05:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T12:58:45.000Z","uid":204943,"like":14,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4537829d927f38675854fbf0a80ebc8b5a2addf4","tid":1128760,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早排我朋友生日約我出街，咁果日咁啱我得閒，我咪出囉。<br />\n<br />\n咁一見面就梗係吹下水咁，點知條00後嘅懵炳喺度同我傾玩具，又咩playoffs又乘咁。<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n00後：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：乜依家玩具玩到咁專業，有playoffs 。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔係玩具黎，真係好認真架。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嘩勁喎，你睇開邊個？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：Curry！(之後係街道射空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屈射遊戲都叫比賽，咁我打飛機世界冠軍啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁...咁都有技術成分嘅...<br />\n<br />\n我聽到即刻火都嚟埋<br />\n一嘢喝鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢俾我嘅氣勢嚇到一嘢跪咗喺度喊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母你地啲00後食屎大定飲尿大<br />\n全部都廢柴嚟，冇撚柒閪用<br />\n我嗰個年代得小朋友先玩呢啲玩具<br />\n18歲都仲玩玩具，俾人屌兩屌就喊到成隻豬咁<br />\n唔怪得之人人都話00後垃圾嚟<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n我先停，放佢一馬<br />\n反正啲低等人種都屌唔醒㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好型"},{"pid":"36ed6ec7373f0740f3a6732cd2798e1a77788a4d","tid":1128760,"uid":113373,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後呼籲</span><br />\n<br />\n撤回修訂《引渡條例》遊行<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年4月28日<br />\n時間：下午3:00集合，4:00起步<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 <br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0aaf89b0259609fc7f4cbddf7915b6c9fae3448","tid":1128760,"uid":15407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"我就真係睇到窒息"},{"pid":"f00cc38a8d26d08e38f3aa774b647076f6e0f0ac","tid":1128760,"uid":1487,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"認真 呢啲post睇得多傷腦"},{"pid":"44199f374dc4327867002f2e484c74302b807775","tid":1128760,"uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f00cc38a8d26d08e38f3aa774b647076f6e0f0ac","tid":1128760,"uid":1487,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"認真 呢啲post睇得多傷腦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"咁你個腦咪好撚廢？"},{"pid":"76d4f4868f190f0c49ad5a6c3c44ed2e2ae3bbe8","tid":1128760,"uid":1487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44199f374dc4327867002f2e484c74302b807775","tid":1128760,"uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f00cc38a8d26d08e38f3aa774b647076f6e0f0ac","tid":1128760,"uid":1487,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"認真 呢啲post睇得多傷腦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"咁你個腦咪好撚廢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"係阿 似足你呢啲波台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889678910c394c586d9edf342c13df3eb72f553f","tid":1128760,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/no